{"word":"ἀναλογίζομαι","slug":"ἀναλογίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναλογίζομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, <i>to reckon up, sum up</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to calculate, consider</i>, <el>τι</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>foll. by a Conj., <el>ἀναλ. ὡς, ὅτι</el>, <i>to recollect</i> that, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}